<p>Comments are always welcome and can be submitted via <strong><a href="https://github.com/uspki/policies/issues/new" target="_blank">this web form</a></strong> (GitHub account required) or sent to: <strong><a href="mailto:fpki@gsa.gov">fpki@gsa.gov</a></strong>.</p>

<h3 id="versions">Versions</h3>

<p><strong>Version 0.1</strong> of this Certificate Policy was opened for comment in September 2017 and closed on October 31, 2017.  All comments received during the comment period were publicly posted <a href="https://github.com/uspki/policies/issues" target="_blank">to this repository</a>.</p>

