  <li><a href="https://github.com/uspki/policies/blob/v0.1/assets/docs/Federal_Public_Trust_Device_PKI_Certificate_Policy_Draft_v0_1_September2017.pdf" target="_blank">PDF copy of Version 0.1</a></li>
